    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">LLMs as cognitive controllers: perception, memory, planning, action, tool use, and collaboration. The full agent stack built on top of frozen weights.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SVG: Agent control loop -->
